text: Julian Soutter (born 20 August 1994) is a South African first-class cricketer. He was included in the North West squad for the 2016 Africa T20 Cup. In September 2018, he was named in Limpopo's squad for the 2018 Africa T20 Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Limpopo cricketers Category:North West cricketers Category:People from Klerksdorp
